creator: lucabilli@grupposervizi.it
text:
Using jakarta-poi-1.9.0-dev-20030122,
I get a warning ([WARNING] Unknown Ptg 29 (41))
parsing an Excel2000 workbook containing a multi-zone named region
(Reference: MySheet!$H$14,MySheet!$I$15).

The following code

HSSFWorkbook wb = new HSSFWorkbook(inputStream);
System.out.println(wb.getNameAt(wb.getNameIndex("MultiArea")).getReference());

besides the above warning, prints:

#REF!

creator: danny@muibros.com
text: i don't believe NamedRegions support multi-zoned regions.

creator: yegor@dinom.ru
text:
Multi-zone names are now supported. Try the latest POI-3.5-beta4. 

Yegor
